         <div class="wrapper">
          <div class="container">
           <div class="hero">
            <img alt="" src="https://sexualrespect.columbia.edu/files/sri/styles/1200x480/public/content/hs_image/2018/50/sexual_respect_matters_cbs_f18_0.jpg?itok=biZNWGE4" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
            <div class="hero-content col-md-8 col-lg-6">
             <h2>
              Welcome to the Sexual Respect Website
             </h2>
             <div class="body">
              <p>
               Here you can find help whenever you need it as well as resources and information about sexual respect in the Columbia community.
               <br/>
               <em>
                Photo of Columbia Business School students, courtesy Halle Morse CBS '20, Fall 2018.
               </em>
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
